      "review_summary": "The PR adds heartbeat-only pending-final replay suppression, active-reply-run guards, and focused regression tests, while also carrying unrelated generated and formatting churn across many files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. I did not run the full Telegram scenario, but current main source shows heartbeat pending-final replay is still possible and the PR body includes a sanitized live Telegram reproduction summary plus terminal proof after the patch.",
